From the ashes of marvel's shield, arrow and the newbie flash rises the making of Gotham's guardian angel. The little Bruce Wayne takes on a very heavy beating on the first season and in the closing episode we can see him man-up to the task of handling control of Wayne enterprises and his intimated friendship with cat-woman. On the streets of Gotham the dark knight challenges and arch rivals are taking birth one by one. The brilliant way they are being crafted will tell you what pure evil means, you will literally be engulfed by each and every characters. First season shows us the rise of penguin and how he creates his own slimy little world. In short this series can make history!